 />\n但開信用卡 借錢就要<br />\n就算呢家開戶要求要SSN 都可以去social security office 攞返個證明話自己唔eligible"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:58:02.000Z","msg":"地址證明都玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}